<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207838>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Semi-schematic line drawings of Aceria argentae n. sp. A. Lateral anterior region; B. Lateral annuli with microtubercles; C. Lateral posterior region; D. Internal female genitalia; E. Empodium; F. Leg I; G. Prodorsal shield; H. Coxigenital region of female. Scale bar: 40 µm for A & C; 20 µm for D, G & H; 10 µm for F; 8 µm for B & E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207838/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207839>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Digital micrographs of the prodorsal shield and coxigenital region of Aceria argentae n. sp. Scale bar: 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207839/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

